@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_citpaa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.04 / v0 + 0.20)) + (0.71 * (v0 + 0.44 + v1 + 0.80)))
    tmp = wp.cos((v1 - v0))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v1 + 0.53) + (tmp + 0.65 / tmp + 0.97)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.86)) * (wp.cos(v0 + 0.14) / (tmp + 0.07 + v2 + 0.73)))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
